==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unlorded
<hw>Un*lord"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <ety>[Properly p. p. of
<ets>unlord</ets>.]</ety> <def>Deprived of the rank of a lord.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> + <ets>lorded</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Not raised to the rank of a lord.</def>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unlove</ent>⟦br⟧
